Explanation.- In computing the aforesaid period of three consecutive months, no account shall be taken of any period of absence with the leave of the Board; or




1013361
chas knowingly contravened the provisions of section 32; or



1146943
dbeing a legal practitioner, acts or appears on behalf of any other person against the Board in any legal proceeding or against the Government in any such proceeding relating to any matter in which the Board is or has been concerned or acts or appears on behalf of any person in any criminal proceeding instituted by or on behalf of the Board against such person; or



64897
