1108021
 35 Consequences of removal.-

1765614
1A member removed under clause (b) of sub- section (1) or under sub- section (3) of section 34 shall, if otherwise qualified, be eligible for re- election or re- nomination. 




460548
2A member removed under clause (c) or clause (d) of sub- section (1) of section 34 shall not be eligible for re- election or nomination for the period during which, but for such removal, he would have continued in office.




359918
