909577
dthe Officer Commanding the station in the cantonment- all buildings and lands, occupied or used for any defence purpose, other than those referred to in clauses (a), (b) and (c);




409087
ethe head of any civil department or railway administration occupying as such any part of the cantonment- all buildings and lands in his charge as head of that department or administration;




988473
fthe head of any establishment or installation of the Defence
Research and Development Organisation in the cantonment- buildings and lands which are occupied or used for the purposes of the Defence Research and Development Organisation in the cantonment;





120666
